OL,6,FJulia Barthram finds out more about a
OL,7,Fnew carbon reducing road surface.
OL,9,FA new material which takes carbon out
OL,10,Fof the atmosphere has been used to
OL,11,Fresurface a North East road in a UK
OL,12,Ffirst.
OL,14,FACLA is a carbon negative aggregate
OL,15,Fwhich permanently stores carbon. It
OL,16,Fcaptures and stores CO2 in the product
OL,17,Fand doesn't release it back out into
OL,18,Fthe atmosphere.
