OL,6,FShe added: "For us, it was, can we
OL,7,Fthink about the carbon footprint and
OL,8,Fthe impact of these materials and
OL,9,Factually do something about it to
OL,10,Fstart decarbonising and achieving net
OL,11,Fzero."
OL,13,FFounded by three PhD students, LCM
OL,14,Fwants to clean up construction.
OL,16,FThe company was shortlisted for 's
OL,17,FEarthshot prize in 2022. The prize
OL,18,Faims to search for the most innovative
OL,19,Fsolutions to the world's greatest
OL,20,Fenvironmental challenges.
