OL,6,F25 million tonnes of asphalt are
OL,7,Fproduced each year (Asphalt Industry
OL,8,FAlliance, 2021). LCM says tackling the
OL,9,Femissions of asphalt is, therefore,
OL,10,Fvital for the UK road network to
OL,11,Fdecarbonise in line with the country's
OL,12,Flegally binding target of achieving
OL,13,Fnet zero by 2050.JIn this trial ACLA
OL,14,Fhas been mixed with recycled plastics,
OL,15,Frubber and asphalt.
OL,17,FThe environmentally friendly road has
OL,18,Fbeen laid by based construction
OL,19,Fcompany MGL Group.
