OL,6,FThe joint chief executive said: "It
OL,7,Flooks and lays exactly like a
OL,8,Fconventional asphalt. People driving
OL,9,Fon this will not notice a difference
OL,10,Fat all, the asphalt that we are laying
OL,11,Ftoday will be the same longevity as a
OL,12,Fnormal asphalt.
OL,14,F"It is so important that we continue
OL,15,Fto look at ways to be as green as
OL,16,Fpossible and help to reduce emissions
OL,17,Ffrom new road construction and
OL,18,Fmaintenance."
